    "• Prepare a small aliquot of a 100 fold dilution of ATP in water • Measure the optical absorbance at 259 nm with a UV-Vis spectrophotometer • Determine the concentration of ATP with an extinction coefficient of 15,400 M -1 cm -1 .",
    "• Adjust volume from step 4 with water that has been sterilly filtered through a 0.22 µm filter"
